**/*.swo

# Cache
**/.cache
**/.eslintcache
**/.stylelintcache
**/.npm
**/.yarn

# Documentation
**/docs
**/*.md
**/LICENSE
**/CHANGELOG.md

# Docker
.docker
**/Dockerfile
**/docker-compose*.yml

# Temporary files
**/tmp
**/temp
**/*.tmp
**/*.temp
**/*.bak

