**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/.debug

# IDE specific files
**/.idea
**/.vscode
**/*.sublime-workspace
**/*.sublime-project
**/.project
**/.classpath
**/.settings
**/.factorypath

# OS generated files
**/.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store?
**/._*
**/.Spotlight-V100
